metadata.name: #1 another pfp
metadata.description: anotherblock brings you another PFP – claimable for our catalog holders (1 pfp per 4 NFTs). the release includes priority access for all drops in season II and an exclusive commercial license to your pfp’s sound loop and artwork. each sound loop is unique and the artwork combines 30+ custom 3d-rendered traits which are inspired by season I. this is our way of saying thank you to our early supporters. democratization of music has only just begun
